{"tid":1686828,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得大學/大專課程好難","createTime":"2019-11-01T11:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T16:17:14.000Z","uid":216357,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"97d2dd91eae8c9f37d05d2fcbf50727abda6e6e2","tid":1686828,"uid":216357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:41:38.000Z","msg":"功課, 考試難度係中學既double, 考試仲要範圍咁大, 一個唔覺意就defer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3a143d57e478151646bce5aadce38b96f95a40","tid":1686828,"uid":277363,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:47:10.000Z","msg":"其實英文唔太差既，真係唔難<br />\n比起中學個啲抄抄寫寫，操技巧<br />\n我寧願用十鳩幾個鐘搵資料<br />\n再用N多時間去慢慢睇essay<br />\n起碼真係學到野同開眼界<br />\n前題就係你本身鐘意個科，就唔會覺得難"},{"pid":"5848c55501af805f01b06985563e97e39608012f","tid":1686828,"uid":220695,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"讀耐咗開始享受做自己鍾意個科嘅assignment<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做到廢寢忘餐都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔鍾意嘅科就眼濕濕咁搞掂佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油呀，黎緊就Exam"},{"pid":"fe2ddf99964a849c6a5f69d5f6ffe25af6ca97fc","tid":1686828,"uid":231131,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:53:55.000Z","msg":"主修課程難啲，只要教個個肯比tips，你又肯背一定合格<br />\n我第一個sem就係冇溫就retake左科<br />\n不過有時唔同lesson啲assignment同test夾埋同一個星期就忙到傻，試過4科aasignment同test逼曬係兩日內。<br />\n所以變相難左，可能上星期教完，下星期就話考<br />\n<br />\n遇上個教得唔好，幾專心上都冇用，keep住讀notes<br />\n我自己遇到兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申讀science既"},{"pid":"4efc4b8d64bf7ab725d7f6ae914c8380f8fbcf21","tid":1686828,"uid":231131,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"最最最重要有past paper就一定要練<br />\n每年既題形都要睇下，捉下佢出咩題目<br />\n就算撞唔中，其他都起碼有練過<br />\n雖然我自己唔係讀大學，只係hd仔<br />\n但讀緊個2年，人地出國旅行，我就留係屋企背野操paper<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新年倒數係溫書中度過<br />\n加油呀！！！靠自己堅持架炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a80dc0d6bb49a2a35fdfac4506c2bc6b26c582c","tid":1686828,"uid":260315,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:05:28.000Z","msg":"難撚到仆晒街，發夢多過上堂，有時間都訓咗，好想defer一年，專心抗爭"},{"pid":"9cb66d0e7058746fdbd1989ad0016921faf7c8e4","tid":1686828,"uid":128164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:44:06.000Z","msg":"覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251cadb1a265a6f191fc15d95c9f9a7a182fe647","tid":1686828,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:51:05.000Z","msg":"難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abe890482a6f9166ff53f1f2b9fcf0e7163d602","tid":1686828,"uid":194248,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a767b43a40387db22e87e4e6b985065121822073","tid":1686828,"uid":21501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:09:52.000Z","msg":"睇咩系<br />\nScience Engine無天份係幾難"},{"pid":"07a6d2e6ae6cf27f668c5fd37ce8875835e9ef49","tid":1686828,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:16:39.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"b05ac77aa7f441b09654ede046462d75ce7c5cda","tid":1686828,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"bb0cc7bd69a1d1a6b5a583a19902dfb9bf280766","tid":1686828,"uid":46823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"今個sem 零舍冇心機讀書<br />\n全部拖到deadline 先開始做<br />\n好在d gpmate 都有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係俾人當freeride"},{"pid":"b0978a4f722e3b26bb91a94821dfb308370ee7b0","tid":1686828,"uid":28702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:29:48.000Z","msg":"我本身英文唔好，<br />\nHD讀工程主要計數唔駛寫太多文章讀得幾爽#<br />\n明白點計條數當做iq題測驗考試都好開心，<br />\n<br />\n到top up讀商科，好多野都要死背，<br />\n又多又難背真心覺得好辛苦&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿sir講明考試每題要寫滿兩版紙，<br />\n當時讀到我心灰意冷，<br />\n讀到要retake幾科決定quit u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後番去讀top up工程輕鬆畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以難唔難好睇你揀唔揀到適合自己既學科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74aa1e02d03264e03f8b413e4ad1ac25e8de29c0","tid":1686828,"uid":324060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"睇你aim咩<br />\n我覺得所有科要碌過其實唔難<br />\n只要你夠努力就得 <br />\n點都好佢唔會F曬所有人<br />\n而總會有10%左右嘅人又蠢又懶<br />\n只要你唔係呢10%就一定唔會肥<br />\n除非你用錯力(e.g.唔明又唔問 自己死刨)<br />\n但有啲科係難高分<br />\n今年有科個lecturer講明會保你pass<br />\n因為唔想太多A比head照肺<br />\n但拎A就一定要又勤力又醒或醒到唔洗溫<br />\n有啲題蠢人係點做都做唔到"},{"pid":"8f7708dfab917f1eb6db25cc58679cf93a595dac","tid":1686828,"uid":134466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:17:14.000Z","msg":"讀理科真係好難。啲數操完都可以唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以最中意讀CC"},{"pid":"a5022b91949d0753f31b7f598ea3c1fe4ef3591b","tid":1686828,"uid":300013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:56:07.000Z","msg":"做assignment還可以。大學係鍛鍊思考方式，唔係填鴨遊戲。已經厭惡死背讀書。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中學辛苦過大學。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油呀。你只係未適應。"},{"pid":"74f2cab5b44d2506d37b6deefd489728cc3d06e1","tid":1686828,"uid":315852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T11:43:03.000Z","msg":"覺，上堂要不停查啲唔識既生字，唔係就一定仆街，啲essay諗點寫諗到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"